<title type="html"><![CDATA[9/4 (Sun.) The Science of Depression / The Types Of Students In Your Class (Host: Ellen)]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=649&amp;p=674#p674"><![CDATA[
9/4 (Sun.) The Science of Depression / The Types Of Students In Your Class (Host: Ellen)<br /><br />Agenda:<br />7:00-7:05 pm Opening Remarks<br />7:05-7:40 pm Session 1: Group Discussion<br />7:40-8:00 pm Individual Presentation<br />8:00-8:05 pm Break<br />8:05-8:35 pm Session 2: Group Discussion<br />8:35-9:00 pm Debate<br /><br />We will hold a zoom meeting only.<br /><br />Zoom meeting: Please click the link below<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw">https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw</a><!-- m --> ...<br />Meeting ID:929 8726 6213<br />Password:112233<br /><br />--------------------------------------------<br /><br />Session I: The Science of Depression<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://tw.voicetube.com/videos/22680">https://tw.voicetube.com/videos/22680</a><!-- m --><br /><br /><br />Questions:<br />1.Have you ever confused of your life or future? What are your confusions? Have your ever talked to others about it? Do you think it’s helpful if you talk to other people about your struggles?<br /><br />2.Do you have seasonal affective disorder(季節性情緒失調)? Which season makes you feel sad or happy? Why?<br /> <br />3.Do you or your friends who ever have depression and go to see the doctor? Did you or they feel better after see the doctor?<br /><br />4.Do you think mental disease is more serious than the physical disease? Why or why not? <br /><br />5.How do you release your stress, depression, or difficulties? Can you share your ways with us?<br /><br />---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />Session II: The Types Of Students In Your Class<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://tw.voicetube.com/videos/45291">https://tw.voicetube.com/videos/45291</a><!-- m --><br /><br /><br />Questions:<br />1.What types of students in your class that you can’t stand of them?<br /><br />2.What types of students in your class that you’re impressed most?<br /><br />3.Have you ever meet a classmate who is very smart or very special in something? Can you share us the story?<br /><br />4.What is the unforgettable thing that you did in your student life? Please share with us.<br /><br />5.If you can back to your student life, what thing that you want to do it again?<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=46353">Ellen Lu</a> — Mon Aug 29, 2022 5:57 pm</p><hr />
]]></content>
